      </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row row--small row--margin row--center">
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 coffee">
        <img src="../public/images/wifiSymbol.jpg" class="coffee__img">
        <h2 class="coffee__name">Services</h2>
        <p class="coffee__descr">
        Get to know what kiosks have WiFi, cold drinks or souvenirs.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 coffee">
        <img src="../public/images/userSymbol.png" class="coffee__img">
        <h2 class="coffee__name">Your own profile</h2>
        <p class="coffee__descr">
          Sign up and have your own account.
        </p>
      </div>
      
       <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4 coffee">
        <img src="../public/images/commentSymbol.jpg" class="coffee__img">
        <h2 class="coffee__name">Comment</h2>
        <p class="coffee__descr">
          Comment about your experience with kiosks you visit.
        </p>
      </div>  
    </div>
       <div class="row row--margin row--center">
         <a href="#" class="btn">Full menu</a>
       </div>
  </div>
</div>

</section>





